      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Turn to Cry</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>No, I never heard her sing, </l>
          <l>Never wondered why </l>
          <l>No, I never meant a thing, </l>
          <l>Never even tried </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>No, she never changed my ways, </l>
          <l>Just watched them swirling by </l>
          <l>I was so tired but never went to bed, </l>
          <l>There was always too much time </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>We had a fast car for a steady pace </l>
          <l>We had to jump start, what was never dead </l>
          <l>And silver linings everywhere, apart from her crystal eyes </l>
          <l>Why they turn out oh-so-fair before they turn to cry?</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
